oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Of My First Love - Harden Trio performance; Childhood Place - Harden Trio performance
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of Of My First Love, produced by Don Law and Frank Jones, recorded in November 1967 at Columbia Recording Studio in Nashville, TN, released by Columbia in 1968, and performed by the Harden Trio. Performance of Childhood Place, written by John Barry Mason and Leslie David Reed, published by Donna Music LTD. and Jewel Music Publishing Co. Inc., produced by Don Law and Frank Jones, recorded on January 26, 1967 at Columbia Recording Studio in Nashville, TN, released by Columbia on March 20, 1967, and performed by the Harden Trio.
